1
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:42,440
Scheme.

2
00:01:04,720 --> 00:01:05,760
What?

3
00:01:06,920 --> 00:01:10,320
You're saying the graves of those young ladies are all empty?

4
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:12,720
How is that possible?

5
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:14,960
And none of the fingerprints match.

6
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:21,980
Could it be that the one who killed Gu and the militia...

7
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,120
The graves are empty.

8
00:01:26,320 --> 00:01:27,980
No fingerprints can be found.

9
00:01:28,400 --> 00:01:30,800
And there are no clues to the murder weapon.

10
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,840
If it weren't for my disbelief in ghosts and spirits,

11
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:33,920
I'm afraid I would suspect

12
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:35,850
it was the work of those dead women.

13
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:40,640
Why do I feel

14
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,520
like we missed something?

15
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:48,800
Female official.

16
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:51,920
Constable Qiu,

17
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,930
when can the case be closed?

18
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:56,120
You are an unmarried woman,

19
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:58,320
and unusually, you became a constable.

20
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,960
It's really inappropriate

21
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:01,800
for you to always hang around Lienv Cliff.

22
00:02:01,800 --> 00:02:02,400
I'm afraid

23
00:02:02,640 --> 00:02:04,840
if you disturb their peaceful cultivation,

24
00:02:04,840 --> 00:02:05,700
the Holy Maiden

25
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,360
will blame me.

26
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:10,850
You are absolutely right, sir.

27
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,160
Then, could you please allow me

28
00:02:12,160 --> 00:02:13,220
to check once more?

29
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:14,960
Haven't you seen it already?

30
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,760
One last time,

31
00:02:16,079 --> 00:02:17,340
so I can close the case.

32
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:19,320
All right.

33
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,220
Did you find anything?

34
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,640
The drillmaster had great martial arts skills.

35
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:58,440
What a pity.

36
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,160
Yes.

37
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,320
A woman wielding weapons

38
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,760
is against feminine virtues in the first place.

39
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:04,520
Moreover,

40
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:06,720
as the drillmaster of Lienv Cliff,

41
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,360
she should have led by example

42
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:10,120
and helped me manage everyone.

43
00:03:10,560 --> 00:03:11,320
But she

44
00:03:11,480 --> 00:03:12,680
was greedy for money,

45
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:15,170
which was why she angered the Holy Maiden.

46
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,560
I just don't know

47
00:03:16,760 --> 00:03:18,640
where her money came from.

48
00:03:20,200 --> 00:03:22,600
Naturally, she extorted it from everyone.

49
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,360
It's also my fault for poor supervision,

50
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,960
giving her the opportunity.

51
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:27,880
Who knew

52
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:29,160
it would harm her?

53
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,320
By the way, Constable Qiu,

54
00:03:34,320 --> 00:03:35,920
are you married?

55
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:38,960
I was before.

56
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:40,800
So you have someone you like.

57
00:03:41,320 --> 00:03:42,520
What do you mean, My Lord?

58
00:03:42,520 --> 00:03:43,920
I just want to advise you,

59
00:03:44,120 --> 00:03:45,200
as a woman,

60
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:47,720
you should abide by the three obediences and four virtues

61
00:03:47,720 --> 00:03:49,840
and focus on your husband and children.

62
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,370
Instead of being like this,

63
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,880
showing your face in public,

64
00:03:52,880 --> 00:03:53,960
accidentally losing your mind,

65
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:55,320
and being tainted by evil.

66
00:03:55,320 --> 00:03:57,120
Then you will be doomed forever.

67
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:00,650
That person never asked this of me.

68
00:04:01,720 --> 00:04:02,480
Instead,

69
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:04,160
he always encouraged me,

70
00:04:04,320 --> 00:04:06,000
supported me, and helped me.

71
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,920
We explored

72
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,920
the truth of the world together.

73
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,040
Being with him,

74
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:15,320
I never lost myself.

75
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:16,970
On the contrary,

76
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:19,959
I knew exactly what I wanted.

77
00:04:20,519 --> 00:04:21,519
So did he.

78
00:04:22,920 --> 00:04:23,720
I think

79
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:26,760
this is the most comfortable relationship between a man and a woman in the world.

80
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:27,440
Never mind.

81
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:30,920
I just wanted to, before I retire,

82
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:32,920
help one more person see the light.

83
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:34,840
That would be a good deed.

84
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:36,420
You are retiring, My Lord?

85
00:04:36,440 --> 00:04:37,320
It's a pity

86
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:39,360
that the good deed is not complete.

87
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,720
There are still people like Gu

88
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,800
and the drillmaster

89
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,960
who are distracted.

90
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:46,120
It will have to be left to the younger generation.

91
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,580
Then I shall take my leave.

92
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:51,200
Please close the case as soon as possible, Constable Qiu.

93
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,600
Did you hear?

94
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:02,640
The female official has retired and returned home.

95
00:05:02,640 --> 00:05:03,960
So, what do you think

96
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,720
the next female official

97
00:05:06,200 --> 00:05:07,360
will be like?

98
00:05:08,840 --> 00:05:10,170
What else can we expect?

99
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:11,560
It's all the same anyway.

100
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,420
Just endure it.

101
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,010
It's a lifetime anyway.

102
00:05:14,280 --> 00:05:16,480
Just grit your teeth and get through it.

103
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:54,330
Husband.

104
00:06:02,600 --> 00:06:03,840
My son died young.

105
00:06:03,880 --> 00:06:05,640
It's all your fault, you jinx.

106
00:06:05,720 --> 00:06:07,200
Why are you still alive?

107
00:06:07,280 --> 00:06:08,320
Why didn't you die with him?

108
00:06:08,320 --> 00:06:09,960
Are you going to remarry?

109
00:06:09,960 --> 00:06:11,800
No, I'm not.

110
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:13,800
Your parents-in-law are dead.

111
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:15,880
You don't need to die to protect your chastity.

112
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,160
I'll give you a place to go.

113
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,760
You will be in charge of it from now on.

114
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:19,800
You just need to

115
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:21,520
provide me with some resources regularly.

116
00:06:21,520 --> 00:06:22,480
Don't worry, My Lord.

117
00:06:22,480 --> 00:06:23,520
The women on Lienü Cliff are all

118
00:06:23,520 --> 00:06:25,320
widows abandoned by their in-laws.

119
00:06:25,320 --> 00:06:28,200
No one will care even if they die.

120
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:31,800
Leave this matter to me.

121
00:06:32,320 --> 00:06:32,960
I promise

122
00:06:33,320 --> 00:06:34,720
no one

123
00:06:34,840 --> 00:06:35,920
will know.

124
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,120
Since things have come to this,

125
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:41,120
it's not easy for you to stop now, My Lord.

126
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,360
Those women have nowhere to go.

127
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,560
We can just find more.

128
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,200
That's right.

129
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:50,560
If we sell these women who faked their deaths,

130
00:06:50,840 --> 00:06:51,680
won't we

131
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,120
still make

132
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:55,560
a fortune?

133
00:07:04,640 --> 00:07:06,640
Why did you lie to me?

134
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,920
Why did you lie to me?

135
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:11,520
Why did you lie to me?

136
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,520
Why did you lie to me?

137
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:16,160
Why did you lie to me?

138
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:16,800
Jinx!

139
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,560
I didn't! It's my fault!

140
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:34,360
It's my fault!

141
00:07:34,360 --> 00:07:35,320
I didn't!

142
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:36,320
I didn't!

143
00:07:36,320 --> 00:07:37,120
What is this?

144
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:39,600
It's my fault.

145
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:41,440
I didn't.

146
00:07:43,760 --> 00:07:45,320
I didn't. It's my fault.

147
00:07:46,920 --> 00:07:48,180
Drugged, as expected.

148
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:54,000
I didn't. I didn't. I didn't.

149
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:56,800
I can't believe she escaped.

150
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:58,440
Did she vanish into thin air?

151
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:27,960
Are you really planning to, for your so-called reputation

152
00:08:27,960 --> 00:08:30,120
be trapped in this hellhole forever?

153
00:08:31,520 --> 00:08:33,679
Is it a sin to be a woman?

154
00:08:33,799 --> 00:08:35,000
Answer me.

155
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:40,780
If your spirit is really here,

156
00:08:41,520 --> 00:08:43,320
open your eyes and look at them.

157
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,160
For your own reputation,

158
00:08:46,160 --> 00:08:47,800
you ruined your entire life.

159
00:08:48,520 --> 00:08:51,440
Do you still want them to suffer like you?

160
00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:54,000
Is this what you really want?

161
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,920
If that is really the case,

162
00:08:57,960 --> 00:09:00,560
you don't deserve to be a saint at all.

163
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,960
Serving husbands and raising kids,

164
00:09:07,960 --> 00:09:09,440
and following strict rules.

165
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,240
Miss Chai.

166
00:09:11,560 --> 00:09:13,760
You who spend your lives for your husbands' families,

167
00:09:13,760 --> 00:09:15,720
should have lived for yourselves.

168
00:09:17,040 --> 00:09:18,770
To hell with your strict rules,

169
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,960
to hell with your laws,

170
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:24,800
and to hell with the shackles that bind women for a lifetime!

171
00:09:24,800 --> 00:09:26,320
I, Chai Yueqing,

172
00:09:28,800 --> 00:09:30,280
refuse to accept this!

173
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,120
Miss Chai.

174
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,360
Miss Chai.

175
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:38,520
You have already done very well.

176
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:40,760
No matter what choice they make,

177
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,320
your appearance

178
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:43,800
will definitely make every single one of them

179
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:45,000
remember you deeply.

180
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:53,440
Look.

181
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:03,240
You lured those widowed women here,

182
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:04,840
selected suitable targets,

183
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:05,970
faked their deaths,

184
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,640
and then secretly sold them.

185
00:10:07,920 --> 00:10:09,320
Where did you take them?

186
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,360
At first,

187
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:13,360
I gave them to the person who saved me.

188
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,920
I never dared to ask.

189
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:18,160
Later, for some reason, he stopped taking people.

190
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:19,360
Tuanlian

191
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:21,120
and Gu found other channels.

192
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:23,080
They handled everything.

193
00:10:23,440 --> 00:10:25,440
I was just responsible for covering up

194
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:27,770
and comforting and intimidating others.

195
00:10:27,920 --> 00:10:29,600
The reason you wanted to retire

196
00:10:29,600 --> 00:10:30,880
was also because those two bodies

197
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,400
died unnatural deaths, right?

198
00:10:32,400 --> 00:10:33,200
No.

199
00:10:33,760 --> 00:10:34,880
Our actions

200
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,560
had always been well hidden.

201
00:10:36,760 --> 00:10:38,400
But after all, it was unconscionable.

202
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:40,440
You'll get your retribution sooner or later.

203
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,170
Sure enough,

204
00:10:41,560 --> 00:10:42,200
Tuanlian

205
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:44,480
and Gu were both punished by heaven.

206
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:46,240
I was afraid if I stayed any longer,

207
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:47,500
I would also become...

208
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:50,440
You threaten others with heavenly punishment all day long,

209
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,640
but you're the one who fears it the most.

210
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:55,240
Save me.

211
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,920
The reason I did those things

212
00:10:58,400 --> 00:11:00,320
was because I wanted to survive.

213
00:11:00,320 --> 00:11:01,520
You want to survive,

214
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:04,000
but what about the women you harmed?

215
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:06,440
They are now living a fate worse than death.

216
00:11:06,440 --> 00:11:08,960
You also almost lost your life because of those ethics,

217
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,640
yet you still use them to harm others.

218
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:11,700
Fooling the world.

219
00:11:11,960 --> 00:11:13,240
I really want to kill you.

220
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:13,720
Qiuyue.

221
00:11:14,120 --> 00:11:15,320
Go back to the county office first.

222
00:11:15,320 --> 00:11:16,720
Bring men to collect the bodies tomorrow.

223
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:18,520
I'll handle the aftermath here.

224
00:11:45,800 --> 00:11:46,640
Miss Gu.

225
00:11:47,720 --> 00:11:50,200
If possible, I really wish I hadn't met you.

226
00:11:50,920 --> 00:11:53,120
At least not in this hellhole.

227
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:59,520
I hope in your next life,

228
00:12:01,040 --> 00:12:02,720
you won't be so miserable.

229
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:28,960
Come in.

230
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:30,800
I've been waiting for you for a long time.
